short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Scan webpage content for indicators and provide.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Welcome to the Cyble Vision | Indicator Search browser plugin! This tool is designed to help you efficiently scan web pages for Indicators of Compromise (IoCs). It detects and provides detailed information about these indicators. 

For Cyble users, the extension offers additional insights into the detected IoCs. Users can also export the information in various formats, including JSON, CSV, TXT, STIX 1.x, and STIX 2.1.
